      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-gray-900">Ergonomic Chair Buying Guide: How to Choose the Right One for Your Body</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">
        Your chair is the single most important purchase in your home office. Here is everything you need to know — what features matter, what to ignore, and which chairs are actually worth your money.
      </p>

